data.description: Seller offering $10,000 flex money with acceptable offer! Newer built home in the growing gated neighborhood of Lafayette Creek Landing right in the heart of Freeport, just behind the Publix complex. This beautiful floor plan features 1820 sq ft, 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, tall ceilings, granite countertops, painted white cabinets, luxury vinyl flooring, a grand master bedroom, back covered patio, and much more. Lafayette Creek Landing has a dock, trail to the creek, and both pool and clubhouse now completed. Even better, you could be within 15 miles from the public beach access at Blue Mountain and all the shops and entertainment that South Walton has to offer. Call today for more details and don't let this one get away.More subdivision info: www.Lafayettecreeklanding.com
